{"title":"Get Your Pie & More with Old Man Mountain’s New Pizza Rack, now with 3-Pack Mounts on the Uprights","link":"https://bikerumor.com/old-man-mountain-new-pizza-rack-3-pack-mounts/","date":1723219200000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-hero.jpeg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" alt=\"(Photos / Old man Mountain)\" /></p>\n<p>I’ve got some tasty news from renowned backpacking and <a href=\"https://oldmanmountain.com/\" target=\"_blank\">rack specialists</a>, Old Man Mountain. It seems that they have listened to all of their customers who’ve been asking for 3-pack mounts on the uprights of the popular, stout Pizza Rack. That’s right, now you can use the Pizza Rack’s large stable platform and cargo cages simultaneously. #ridebikesbringstuff</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-full-bike.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-full-bike.jpeg\" alt=\"Old Man Mountain New Pizza Rack full bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-full-bike.jpeg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-full-bike-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-full-bike-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-full-bike-768x768.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Old Man Mountain)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Pizza Rack has all the necessary hardware to mount the rack to your fork’s eyelets. If your trusty steed doesn’t have the eyelets needed, it’s cool. The Pizza Rack can attach to the axle via the Old Man Mountain <a href=\"https://oldmanmountain.com/fit-kits-and-spare-parts/\" target=\"_blank\">Fit-Kits</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-3-pack-mounts.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-3-pack-mounts.jpeg\" alt=\"Old Man Mountain New Pizza Rack 3-pack mounts\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-3-pack-mounts.jpeg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-3-pack-mounts-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-3-pack-mounts-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-3-pack-mounts-768x768.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Fit-Kits can be mounted to suspension forks, carbon, steel, or aluminum forks.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-with-OMM-Basket.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-with-OMM-Basket.jpeg\" alt=\"Old Man Mountain New Pizza Rack with OMM Basket\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-with-OMM-Basket.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-with-OMM-Basket-297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-with-OMM-Basket-120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-with-OMM-Basket-768x576.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-poter-bag-on-the-go.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-poter-bag-on-the-go.jpeg\" alt=\"Old Man Mountain New Pizza Rack poter bag on the go\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-poter-bag-on-the-go.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-poter-bag-on-the-go-297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-poter-bag-on-the-go-120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-poter-bag-on-the-go-768x576.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>However, if want to ramp up said bike’s versatility, then you’ll be happy to know that the Pizza Rack pairs very well with the popular <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/old-man-mountain-basket-pannier-trunk-axle-pack-for-suspension-forks/\" target=\"_blank\">OMM Basket</a>. Plus, it works well with a Carracice porter bag as well. The new Pizza Rack utilizes stiffer, heavier-duty versions of the “Y” shaped uprights that you’d find on the<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/old-man-mountains-ekhorn-available-for-preorder-now/\" target=\"_blank\"> Elkhorn Rack</a>. This allows for a weight rating of 35 lbs.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-large-strong-platform.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-large-strong-platform.jpeg\" alt=\"Old Man Mountain New Pizza Rack large strong platform\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-large-strong-platform.jpeg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-large-strong-platform-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-large-strong-platform-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-large-strong-platform-768x768.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-large-platform.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-large-platform.jpeg\" alt=\"Old Man Mountain New Pizza Rack large platform\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-large-platform.jpeg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-large-platform-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-large-platform-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-large-platform-768x768.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Old man Mountain)</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Pizza Rack Retail &amp; Specs</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $188</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-coke.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-coke.jpeg\" alt=\"Old Man Mountain New Pizza Rack coke\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-coke.jpeg 960w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-coke-225x300.jpeg 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-coke-90x120.jpeg 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-coke-768x1024.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Pizza Rack is designed for use with 700c or 27.5′ sized wheels. It can fit tires up to 700c x 50mm. <em>(371mm from the mounting point to the underside of the deck). </em></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Front mountable<a href=\"https://news.twotoneams.nl/240166-old-man-mountain-new-pizza-rack#\"></a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>3-pack mounts on the uprights <a href=\"https://news.twotoneams.nl/240166-old-man-mountain-new-pizza-rack#\"></a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fits up to 157mm wide hubs<a href=\"https://news.twotoneams.nl/240166-old-man-mountain-new-pizza-rack#\"></a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Made from 6061 aluminum </li>\n\n\n\n<li>The rack frame is made of 13 mm diameter tubing<a href=\"https://news.twotoneams.nl/240166-old-man-mountain-new-pizza-rack#\"></a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>The deck measures 326mm x 255mm<a href=\"https://news.twotoneams.nl/240166-old-man-mountain-new-pizza-rack#\"></a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Height from the mounting point to the deck is 378mm<a href=\"https://news.twotoneams.nl/240166-old-man-mountain-new-pizza-rack#\"></a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>The deck includes slots for easily lashing gear in place and holes for a light mount<a href=\"https://news.twotoneams.nl/240166-old-man-mountain-new-pizza-rack#\"></a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Comes with standard, eyelet mount ready with optional fit kits available for thru axle or QR mounting<a href=\"https://news.twotoneams.nl/240166-old-man-mountain-new-pizza-rack#\"></a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Load capacity of 15.8kg<a href=\"https://news.twotoneams.nl/240166-old-man-mountain-new-pizza-rack#\"></a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Backed by a Lifetime Warranty</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-holding-pizzas.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-holding-pizzas.jpeg\" alt=\"Old Man Mountain New Pizza Rack holding pizzas\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-holding-pizzas.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-holding-pizzas-297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-holding-pizzas-120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Old-Man-Mountain-New-Pizza-Rack-holding-pizzas-768x576.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out all of the items to help you bring stuff along with you on your next bike ride, bikepacking adventure, or a trip to the store at the link below.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://oldmanmountain.com/\">OldManMountain.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/old-man-mountain-new-pizza-rack-3-pack-mounts/\">Get Your Pie &amp; More with Old Man Mountain’s New Pizza Rack, now with 3-Pack Mounts on the Uprights</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"b063e0b513605e66830f6f2ae1b1db5d4e8c47031227fe1c46bf0035bdc9637f","category":"Cycling"}